Interface AHContactPersistence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.liferay.portal.service.persistence.BasePersistence<AHContact>

    public interface AHContactPersistence
extends com.liferay.portal.service.persistence.BasePersistence<AHContact>
    The persistence interface for the a h contact service.

    Caching information and settings can be found in portal.properties

      • findByemail

        List<AHContact> findByemail(String email,
                          int start,
                          int end)
                            throws com.liferay.portal.kernel.exception.SystemException
        Returns a range of all the a h contacts where email = ?.

        Useful when paginating results. Returns a maximum of end - start instances. start and end are not primary keys, they are indexes in the result set. Thus, 0 refers to the first result in the set. Setting both start and end to QueryUtil.ALL_POS will return the full result set. If orderByComparator is specified, then the query will include the given ORDER BY logic. If orderByComparator is absent and pagination is required (start and end are not QueryUtil.ALL_POS), then the query will include the default ORDER BY logic from de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.particity.model.impl.AHContactModelImpl. If both orderByComparator and pagination are absent, for performance reasons, the query will not have an ORDER BY clause and the returned result set will be sorted on by the primary key in an ascending order.

        Parameters:
        email - the email
        start - the lower bound of the range of a h contacts
        end - the upper bound of the range of a h contacts (not inclusive)
        Returns:
        the range of matching a h contacts
        Throws:
        SystemException - if a system exception occurred
